s/plugged-in/saints-win-super-bowl-says-madden-nfl/1387788|archivedate=13 February 2010}}</ref>\n|- style=\"background:#fcc;\"\n|2011\n|align=\"left\"| [[Super Bowl XLV|XLV]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[2010 Pittsburgh Steelers season|Pittsburgh Steelers]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[2010 Green Bay Packers season|Green Bay Packers]]\n|25 \u2013 31 ||24 \u2013 20 ||{{n}} ||{{n}} ||6\u20132\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blog.games.yahoo.com/blog/355-steelers-will-win-super-bowl-xlv-predicts-madden-11;_ylt=A2KIRkzLgUhNxnQBFQBfzssh|title=Yahoo|publisher=|accessdate=15 June 2016}}</ref>\n|- style=\"background:#cfc;\"\n|2012\n|align=\"left\"| [[Super Bowl XLVI|XLVI]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[2011 New York Giants season|New York Giants]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[2011 New England Patriots season|New England Patriots]]\n|21 \u2013 17 ||27 \u2013 24 ||{{y}} ||{{n}} ||7\u20132\n|<ref>{{cite news | author = Doug Aamoth | url=http://techland.time.com/2012/01/30/madden-nfl-12-simulates-super-bowl-last-second-kick-wins-it-all/ | title = Madden NFL 12 Simulates Super Bowl \u2013 Last-Second Kick Wins It All | work=Time | date=2012-01-30}}</ref>\n|- style=\"background:#cfc;\"\n|2013\n|align=\"left\"| [[Super Bowl XLVII|XLVII]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[2012 Baltimore Ravens season|Baltimore Ravens]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[2012 San Francisco 49ers season|San Francisco 49ers]]\n|34 \u2013 31 ||27 \u2013 24 ||{{y}} ||{{y}} ||8\u20132\n|<ref>{{cite news| url=http://kotaku.com/5979451/madden-right-in-7-of-its-last-9-picks-says-baltimore-wins-super-bowl-xlvii | title = Madden, Right In 7 of Its Last 9 Picks, Says Baltimore Wins Super Bowl XLVII | work=Time | date=2013-01-28}}</ref>\n|- style=\"background:#fcc;\"\n|2014\n|align=\"left\"| [[Super Bowl XLVIII|XLVIII]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[2013 Denver Broncos season|Denver Broncos]]\n|align=\"left\"| [[2013 Seattle Seahawks season|Seattle Seahawks]]\n|8 \u2013 43 ||31 \u2013 28 ||{{n}} ||{{n}} ||8\u20133\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://games.yahoo.com/blogs/plugged-in/broncos-win-s