hort film\n|-\n| rowspan=2|2009\n| ''[[Boogie Woogie (film)|Boogie Woogie]]''\n| Alfreda Rhinegold\n|\n|-\n|''[[Professor Layton and the Eternal Diva]]''\n| Stella\n| English version\n|-\n| 2010\n|''[[Animals United]]''\n| Giselle\n| Voice (English version)\n|-\n| 2011\n| ''[[Late Bloomers (2011 film)|Late Bloomers]]''\n| Charlotte\n|\n|-\n|2012\n|Europe's Last Dictator\n|Narrator\n|Documentary\n|-\n| rowspan=2|2013\n| ''[[The Wolf of Wall Street (2013 film)|The Wolf of Wall Street]]''\n| Aunt Emma\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Gangsta Granny (film)|Gangsta Granny]]''\n| [[Elizabeth II]]\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=2|2014\n| ''Death Knight Love Story''\n| Lady Blameaux\n| Voice\n|-\n| ''[[She's Funny That Way (film)|She's Funny That Way]]''\n| Vivian Claremont\n| \n|-\n| 2015\n| ''[[Absolutely Anything]]''\n| Fenella\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=2|2016\n| ''[[Me Before You (film)|Me Before You]]''\n| Mary Rawlinson\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Absolutely Fabulous: The Movie]]''\n| [[Patsy Stone]]\n| \n|-\n| rowspan=4|2017\n| ''The Man You're Not''\n| Joanna Lumley\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Paddington 2]]''\n| Felicity Fanshaw\n|\n|-\n| ''And the Winner Isn't''\n| Herself\n| Documentary\n|-\n| ''[[Finding Your Feet]]''\n| Jackie\n| \n|-\n| 2020\n| ''[[The Croods 2]]''\n| Queen Ofeilia\n| ''In-Production''\n|}\n\n===Television===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n!class=\"unsortable\" |Notes\n|-\n| 1969\n| ''[[The Wednesday Play]]''\n| Elsie Engelfield\n| 1 episode\n|-\n| 1971\n| ''[[It's Awfully Bad For Your Eyes, Darling]]''\n| Samantha Ryder-Ross\n|\n|-\n| 1972\n| ''[[Steptoe and Son]]''\n| Bunty\n| Episode: \"Loathe Story\"\n|-\n| 1973\n| ''[[Coronation Street]]''\n| [[Elaine Perkins]]\n| 8 episodes\n|-\n| 1973\u201375\n| ''[[Are You Being Served?]]''\n| Miss French / German Lady\n| 2 episodes: \"His and Hers\"/\"German Week\"\n|-\n| 1976\n| ''[[The Cuckoo Waltz]]''\n| Harriet Paulden\n| Episode: \"Babysitter'\"\n|-\n| 1976\u201377\n| ''[[The New Avengers (TV series)|The New Avengers]]''\n| Purdey